commentText: Constructs a new instance of the StaxStreamXmlReader that reads from the given_XMLStreamReader. The supplied stream reader must be in XMLStreamConstants.START_DOCUMENT_or XMLStreamConstants.START_ELEMENT state.__@param reader the XMLEventReader to read from_@throws IllegalStateException if the reader is not at the start of a document or element
codeText: StaxStreamXMLReader(XMLStreamReader reader) {_		Assert.notNull(reader, "'reader' must not be null")__		int event = reader.getEventType()__		if (!(event == XMLStreamConstants.START_DOCUMENT || event == XMLStreamConstants.START_ELEMENT)) {_			throw new IllegalStateException("XMLEventReader not at start of document or element")__		}_		this.reader = reader__	}
